[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/weak_2s"]
[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

With 10 points and a great 6-card suit this is a perfect Weak 2-Bid. You open 2\D. East passes and partner jumps to 4\D. West passes.  

This is not an invitation to bid game. If partner had game interest he would bid 2NT. Apparently he is trying to preempt the opponents out of their hand and apparently it is working. You pass.}

