[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

You open with a Weak 2-Bid, 2\H. Partner responds 2\S. What do you say next? 

The 2\S bid is forcing for one round, but you want to bid again anyway. While you had an 11 point hand when you opened 2\H it has actually grown in value in support of \Ss. It is a question whether you should now bid 3\S or 4\S. Let's assume you say 3\S and partner raises to 4\S.}

